# SAM Master Extract Mapping (February 2025)

Last Updated: 2025-02-13

## Data Element Mapping

| # | Element | Datatype | Format | Max Len | Definition | Mandatory | Sensitivity |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | UNIQUE ENTITY ID | STRING | ALPHANUMERIC | 12 | The UNIQUE ENTITY ID for the entity. It is 12-character alpha-numeric. Example: F847A1795DE4 | If Available (All Awards/Federal Assistance) | Public |
| 2 | BLANK (DEPRECATED) | STRING | STRING |  | Blank Spaces, formerly occupied by the prior Entity identifier |  | Public |
| 3 | ENTITY EFT INDICATOR | STRING | STRING | 4 | See SAM Functional Data Dictionary | Optional | Public |
