| 7 | PURPOSE OF REGISTRATION | STRING | STRING | 2 | See SAM Functional Data Dictionary | Mandatory | Public |
| 8 | INITIAL REGISTRATION DATE | STRING | YYYYMMDD | 8 | The date the initial entity registration was activated either in SAM or its predecessor, CCR. This date does not change. | Mandatory | Public |
