### NAICS Code String

Format: `~NAICS_CODE + SMALL_BIZ_INDICATOR~` (repeating)

Example: `~237990N~541340N~`

- Position 1: NAICS Code (6 digits)
- Position 2: Small Business Indication (Y/N)

### PSC Code String

Format: `~PSC_CODE~` (repeating)

Example: `~Y159~Y161~Y162~Z200~Z300~`

